    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and visible fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, but all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for reliable transportation at an affordable price point.",
