    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term mechanical integrity, the rod bearings have been replaced and the VANOS system has been fully overhauled. The chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in and lateral stability these cars are known for. While the aesthetics show minor signs of use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including the cooling system and valve clearances\u2014are meticulously maintained for optimal performance.",
