      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of pride of ownership, offering a reliable and polished driving experience. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, having been regularly hand-washed and waxed; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper from normal highway use, the body is straight and free of any significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seats have been treated regularly to prevent cracking, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats. All interior electronics, including the premium sound system, navigation, and heated seats, are in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It features a complete service history with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. Most recently, the vehicle underwent a full multi-point inspection, receiving new brake pads and a fresh set of tires. The engine runs quietly, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. This is a turn-key car ready for its next chapter, offering a premium feel at a sensible price point.",
